# InferTest — expected entailments
# Construct : rdfs:subClassOf (class subsumption)
#
# These triples MUST be present in the reasoner's inferred closure after
# loading premises.ttl (optionally merged with your own ontology).
# The validator (scripts/run_all_tests.py) checks each one individually.

@prefix : <http://example.org/infertest#> .
@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .
@prefix rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .

### Rex is a Dog and Dog is a subclass of Animal -> Rex must be typed Animal.
:Subclass_Rex rdf:type :Subclass_Animal .
